{
  "stem": "13258.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And for two days, we were standing on that station.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "For the first 12 or more hours, we didn't even get a bucket of water to drink.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was one baby in our compartment which was being still nourished by its mother.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They allowed some people from the city, from my father's company, they came, and-- with the payroll, and my father got some money.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And some other people got some money.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They allowed that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But otherwise, from that one side of the train, they were checking who was-- and they were allowing a few people.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "On the other side of the train, soldiers with carbines and bayonets on the carbines, were patrolling, going forward and back, which did not hinder certain people from the city to come in.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And when the soldier was going this way, they [? snuck ?] to somebody here.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And when they come the other way, they knew they wouldn't shoot.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I mean, that cruel, they hadn't been yet at that time, at least.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And so a girlfriend I had met over there came to me three times.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "She brought me food, she brought me something to drink, because we were thirsty.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was hot.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "She climbed over fences.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "She got in between freight trains, under the trains, and so on, and other people also were getting stuff there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But the next night, a [? rainy ?] night, suddenly the doors opened, and two officers came.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And he said, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "That means bachelors-- bachelors or bachelorettes-- out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They considered a bachelor, at the time, anybody who was not with a family, a wife.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my father said, we are not bachelors.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We are family together.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so did a couple of our other friends who were brothers or so.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "From our car, nobody left.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
